{"tid":1346963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣傳 光復紅磡土瓜灣 讓路改期至8.17","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:23.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afbbb95203d520c9e1026ce969658d5c9029f2f5","tid":1346963,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"請廣傳：「光復紅土」遊行改期至 817<br />\n<br />\n七月廿一日晚上，元朗包括港鐵元朗站發生白衣黑幫份子無差別攻擊途人的恐佈事件；對於鄉黑勢力的暴行和警方刻意包庇導致多人受傷，全港市民同表憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n即日深夜，一班有心的元朗居民發起七月廿八日舉行元朗區公眾活動；就此， 發起「光復紅土　還我淨土」遊行的一眾街坊在「公海」群組，投票決定將遊行由 7 月 27 日延期至 8 月 17 日。<br />\n<br />\n身為遊行的不反對通知書申請人，我尊重和認同上述決定，並會在申請不反對通知書及與當局協調的工作上全面配合改期的安排，而紅土區的遊行路線、起點、終點暫時不變。<br />\n<br />\n天祐香港。<br />\n<br />\n#真係暫緩 #唔係撤回 #817約定你"},{"pid":"eb0a128838b10acaaf5b7cf72bf5ad779dbe9bd6","tid":1346963,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b509dfa39ec3f10fe5861ab338103b7e739ce35","tid":1346963,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf6e584369a8f6d38bd489abe4123e5080e37af","tid":1346963,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察鄉黑 上環元朗 分工合作 暴打市民 無法無天</span></span>"},{"pid":"a59e2c6b03a8afa431bff9584911ba86f556d70c","tid":1346963,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3ff6ba996bb5302f9ea4df252ed3c46e8f8309","tid":1346963,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 